    author: 'John Smith',
    slug: 'cybersecurity-best-practices-remote-work',
  },
  {
    title: 'Leveraging AI for Business Intelligence',
    excerpt:
      'Discover how artificial intelligence is revolutionizing business intelligence and decision-making processes.',
    image: '/service3.jpg',
    date: 'June 20, 2023',
    author: 'Emily Chen',
    slug: 'leveraging-ai-business-intelligence',
  },
  {
    title: 'The Rise of Edge Computing in IoT',
    excerpt:
      'Understand how edge computing is transforming IoT applications and improving data processing efficiency.',
    image: '/service4.jpg',
    date: 'July 5, 2023',
    author: 'Michael Johnson',
    slug: 'rise-of-edge-computing-iot',
  },
  {
